      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-brand-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
        CUET UG 2026 · Batches Open
